    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在枪林弹雨、血肉模糊的战场上随着音乐的节奏起舞吧！</h2><strong>《KILLBEAT》</strong> 是一款节奏射击Roguelike游戏，主打节奏快速、粗暴血腥且考验技术的游戏内容。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/7f368dc2c098f609930403739e1a3665.poster.avif?t=1748541944\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/7f368dc2c098f609930403739e1a3665.webm?t=1748541944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/7f368dc2c098f609930403739e1a3665.mp4?t=1748541944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>射击，冲刺，一路随着节拍横扫敌人。<br></li><li>收集自由式次数，创造出你自己想要的节奏。<br></li><li>在随机生成的游戏世界中，体验支线故事。<br></li><li>和其他玩家创造并分享自制音乐组合包。<br></li><li>和好友竞技，进行每日和每周挑战。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在这颗星球的核心深处</h2>有个神一般的生物苏醒了。它的存在使“节奏深渊”为之颤抖，这便是地面因为震动而分裂形成的峡谷。投身这个混乱的战场，你扮演其中一名幸存者，你能够听见来自星球地底深处的呼喊……也是唯一胆敢前去一探究竟的勇者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/3d202bcf2ec4dd3724fd04368e92d414.poster.avif?t=1748541944\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/3d202bcf2ec4dd3724fd04368e92d414.webm?t=1748541944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/3d202bcf2ec4dd3724fd04368e92d414.mp4?t=1748541944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >攻击就是最好的防御</h2>一路往下探险，并横扫怪物和头目，进行支线故事遭遇战，不断深入地底，随着节奏找到节拍的来源。你在故事剧情中所做的决定，会在你更深入地底后产生影响。<br><br>探索随机生成的关卡，享受节奏导向且讲究技术的游戏内容。顺着节拍射击，冲刺、装填并终结敌人吧。每次闯关都可搭配出不同的组合和流派，并在中枢解锁全新物品和武器，那里是人类文明历经摧残后的最终堡垒，就位于“节奏深渊”的边缘。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/3f3ed3b31cc486e2ad70c27a5ef9c440.poster.avif?t=1748541944\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/3f3ed3b31cc486e2ad70c27a5ef9c440.webm?t=1748541944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104040/extras/3f3ed3b31cc486e2ad70c27a5ef9c440.mp4?t=1748541944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >顺着节奏起舞</h2>《KILLBEAT》原声带的创作灵感源自于电音舞曲和金属乐，并添加了洗脑的人声旋律，创造出独特的风格。徜徉在美妙的音乐中，保持连击不中断，并为曲目添加更多乐器，可在游戏中获得奖励。你也可通过自定义音乐功能转换节奏。",
